# This version uses `xkblayout-state` to get and set keyboard layouts
#

### 
### Originals
###
### i3-keyboard-layout
### https://github.com/porras/i3-keyboard-layout
### 
### Tazeg/i3status
### https://github.com/Tazeg/i3status  
